1) I created python virtual environment via:
python3 -m venv ~/repos/Halloween2024_HogwartsExpress/halloween2024_venv

2) activate it using:
source halloween2024_venv/bin/activate

3) confirm the virtual env via:
which python

4) deactivate virtual env, when you're in it, via:
deactivate


packages to install

pip3 install python-vlc
pip3 install sanic # used for async HTML calls
pip3 install sanic aiohttp
pip3 install pyserial
